2.1 Hot-plug protocol
Discovery: Searxng RSS poll â†’ new ggml file appears in Ollama cloud repo.
Benchmark-MCP:
Downloads model (range-request first 500 MB) â†’ streams 3 micro-tasks (math, code, chat).
Computes embedding alignment score vs existing swarm (â‰¤5 % drift = safe).
