Auto-go-live: If p95 latency â‰¤ 120 % of pool median and quality â‰¥ 90 % of best model â†’ added to rotation; else quarantined for manual review.
Entire cycle <30 min; zero dropped requests.

2.2 Model-specific gem profiles (auto-generated)
